description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION
The BLONDME Lightener and Colour range provide the high performance needed to create personalized blonde looks. It is specially formulated to partner BLONDME bleach and colour shades. What it does: Premium Care Developer offer up to 9 levels of lift while the readytouse toners and white blending shades give endless creative potential for blonde hair. Its an oil developer formula that maintains hair's natural moisture to ensure your blondes have brilliant shine and a wonderfully soft feel to their hair.

FEATURES
Lifts on natural base 6 7
Premium hair developer
Oilin formula
Maintains the hair's natural moisture balance
Smooths the hair surface

HOW TO USE
Mix the developer with the BlondMe Bond Enforcing Powder using the proper ratio.
Section the hair.
Apply on small section of hair at a time.
Leave out 1.5 centimeters from the scalp.
Use plenty of product to insure full saturation.
Use the remaining product on the roots.
Rinse thoroughly.
Shampoo with BLONDME Keratin Restore Bonding Shampoo.
Apply toner as desired.

product_name: @DM 330ml HOLD ME Three Ways Hairspray CR12
description:
DESCRIPTION

Provide 3 levels of hold: light, medium, high hold in 1 can - without the crunch.

- Light hold (2/10 hold level) – Ideal for prepping hair and getting rid of annoying flyaways

- Medium hold (5/10 hold level)– Flexible yet long-lasting hold, perfect as a working spray

- High hold (8/10 hold level) – Locks in your look with a firm yet touchable hold

FEATURES

Provide 3 levels of hold: light, medium, high hold in 1 can - without the crunch.

HOW TO USE

Twist nozzle to the desired hold, shake well and spray on dry hair.

DESCRIPTION

It's time to satisfy your craving for volume. This airy mousse transforms hair, giving it noticeable volume & bounce from roots to ends. It features a whipped, foamy texture that easily works into the hair for a strong, long-lasting hold, without any stickiness or crunch. Bonus: PUFF.ME’s formula multi-tasks to protect your hair from heat and lightly hydrate for the perfect amount of added shine and softness. Big hair has never looked this good.Builds weightless volume, body & bounceStrong, flexible hold keeps the volume up all day (and all night)Multi-tasking formula conditions while building volume for added shine Designed with built-in heat & humidity protection

FEATURES

Transforms hair, giving it noticeable volume & bounce from roots to ends. It features a whipped, foamy texture that easily works into the hair for a strong, long-lasting hold, without any stickiness or crunch.

HOW TO USE

Apply 1-2 palm fulls into damp hair. Blow dry & style as normal.

DESCRIPTION:

Framar’s Dreamweaver combs are intricately designed to save time behind the chair and shave hours off highlighting applications. Weave on!

UPS:680343920007

Work through wet, clean hair. Use sparingly near roots and more liberally towards ends. Leave on for 1 to 3 minutes before rinsing. For additional conditioning on severely damaged hair, wrap conditioned hair in warm towelsor set under heat lamps for an additional 1 to 3 minutes. Rinse well and style as normal.

description:
DESCRIPTION
It's a Ten Miracle Blowdr Volumizer gives hair a little extra lift, without the sticky, heavy hold of traditional hairspray. Our flexible, multipurpose formula conditions, controls, and adds bounce and volume without leaving any trace onfinished strands.

FEATURES
1. Explosive volume
2. Adds shine
3. Humidity resistant
4. Buildup free
5. Medium hold factor
6. Safe for coloured hair
7. Non-flaking
8. Helps achieve touchable thickness
9. Lightweight
10. Non-drying

HOW TO USE
Spray generously on to clean, damp hair prior to styling. Focus on roots and work evenly through to ends. Do not rinse or spritz with water. Style as desired and finish with another generous spray to hold style. For extra volume, blow dry upside down or use velcro rollers at crown, near scalp.

DESCRIPTION
Restorative formulas infused with argan oil and nourishing ingredients for healthy and strong hair. Moisture repair shampoo and conditioner are for hair that has been weakened or damaged by color, chemical processing, or heat styling. They restore hair by bathing it in a highly concentrated formula rich in antioxidant argan oil, reconstructive keratin, and fatty acids, this moisturizing shampoo mends broken strands and dead ends to restore elasticity, moisture, and shine.


FEATURES
Restore elasticity, moisture, and manageability
Won’t dry, fade or strip colortreated hair
Highly concentrated formula
Free of sulfate, phosphate, and paraben
Safer for the environment


HOW TO USE
Massage throughout wet hair and scalp
Continue to add water to activate a rich lather
Rinse thoroughly until water runs clear
Repeat if needed
Follow with Moroccanoil Moisture Repair conditioner

product_name: BlondMe Bond Enforcing Premium Lift 9+ Lightener 450g CR6
description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION

Blondme Bond Enforcing Premium Lightener 9+ is a high performance powder lightener. This is the first powder lightener to provide up to 9 levels of lift on natural and coloured hair. It offers perfect neutralisation thanks to it's antiyellowagents which directly target the pheomelanin in hair to avoid unwanted warm or yellow undertones.

FEATURES
Integrated bonding technology
Up to 9 levels of lift
Helps to protect the hair fiber during development for minimized hair breakage
Antiyellow agents to neutralize any warm undertones
Flexible mixing ratio
Easy workable consistency
Suitable for all technique

HOW TO USE
Always use in combination with BLONDME® Premium Developers.
Mix 1:1.5 to 1:2.5 (Ex: 30g BLONDME Premium Lightener 9+ and 4575 mL BLONDME Premium Developer).
OnScalp Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 2% (7 Vol.) or 6% (20 Vol.).
Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 9% (30 Vol.).
Apply to dry hair and let develop for 20 to 45 minutes.
Additional heat is not recommended.
Visually check progress during development time.

PROTIP
For gentle lightening and optimal time control, use BLONDME Premium Developer 2% (7 Vol.).
Check visually every 5 minutes.

description:

DESCRIPTION
This claybased powder lightener allows a precise application. The creamy consistency allows a smooth application and a seamless result. Thanks to the creamtosolid formula, the upper layer hardens and traps the moisture to ensure optimal lightening while protecting the rest of the hair from transfer.

FEATURES
Claybased lightener
With bond enforcing technology
Perfect for freehand lightening service
Up to 7 level of lift
Softtosolid formula

HOW TO USE
Use with the BlondMe Premium Developper
Ratio of 1: 1.5 or 1: 2 depending on the desired consistency
Apply on dry hair without additional heat

It offers perfect neutralisation thanks to it's antiyellowagents which directly target the pheomelanin in hair to avoid unwanted warm or yellow undertones.

FEATURES
Integrated bonding technology
Up to 9 levels of lift
Helps to protect the hair fiber during development for minimized hair breakage
Antiyellow agents to neutralize any warm undertones
Flexible mixing ratio
Easy workable consistency
Suitable for all technique

HOW TO USE
Always use in combination with BLONDME® Premium Developers.
Mix 1:1.5 to 1:2.5 (Ex: 30g BLONDME Premium Lightener 9+ and 4575 mL BLONDME Premium Developer).
OnScalp Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 2% (7 Vol.) or 6% (20 Vol.).
Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 9% (30 Vol.).
Apply to dry hair and let develop for 20 to 45 minutes.
Additional heat is not recommended.
Visually check progress during development time.

PROTIP
For gentle lightening and optimal time control, use BLONDME Premium Developer 2% (7 Vol.).
Check visually every 5 minutes.

description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION
The BLONDME Lightener and Colour range provide the high performance needed to create personalized blonde looks. It is specially formulated to partner BLONDME bleach and colour shades. What it does: Premium Care Developer offer up to 9 levels of lift while the readytouse toners and white blending shades give endless creative potential for blonde hair. Its an oil developer formula that maintains hair's natural moisture to ensure your blondes have brilliant shine and a wonderfully soft feel to their hair.

FEATURES
Lifts on natural base 6 7
Premium hair developer
Oilin formula
Maintains the hair's natural moisture balance
Smooths the hair surface

HOW TO USE
Mix the developer with the BlondMe Bond Enforcing Powder using the proper ratio.
Section the hair.
Apply on small section of hair at a time.
Leave out 1.5 centimeters from the scalp.
Use plenty of product to insure full saturation.
Use the remaining product on the roots.
Rinse thoroughly.
Shampoo with BLONDME Keratin Restore Bonding Shampoo.
Apply toner as desired.

DESCRIPTION
Schwarzkopf Igora Royal Permanent colour provides total coverage and intensity while maintaining scalp comfort. Its formula allows to equalize the colour evenly even on porous hair. The pigment penetrates the hair efficiently and is locked in for longlasting, vibrant colour.

FEATURES
Permanent hair colour.
Covers white air up to 100%.
Longlasting colour retention.
Intense colour vibrancy.
Works even on porous hair.
Absolute truetotuft results.

HOW TO USE
Mix the colour and developer at a ratio of 1: 1 for a normal colouring, or 1: 2 for a lighter shade.
VIRGIN HAIR: apply the mixture to lengths and ends, then to roots after 15 to 20 minutes.
COLOURED HAIR: apply the mixture to the regrowth, then to the lengths and tips after 15 to 30 minutes.
Leave as directed on instructions.
Rinse thoroughly, then wash and condition the hair.

product_name: 12-21 Highlift Special Blonde With FIBERPLEX Igora Royal JA2022
description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION
Schwarzkopf Igora Royal Permanent colour provides total coverage and intensity while maintaining scalp comfort. Its formula allows to equalize the colour evenly even on porous hair. The pigment penetrates the hair efficiently and is locked in for longlasting, vibrant colour.

FEATURES
Permanent hair colour.
Covers white air up to 100%.
Longlasting colour retention.
Intense colour vibrancy.
Works even on porous hair.
Absolute truetotuft results.

HOW TO USE
Mix the colour and developer at a ratio of 1: 1 for a normal colouring, or 1: 2 for a lighter shade.
VIRGIN HAIR: apply the mixture to lengths and ends, then to roots after 15 to 20 minutes.
COLOURED HAIR: apply the mixture to the regrowth, then to the lengths and tips after 15 to 30 minutes.
Leave as directed on instructions.
Rinse thoroughly, then wash and condition the hair.

product_name: 5-16 Light Brown Centre Chocolate Igora Royal
description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION
Schwarzkopf Igora Royal Permanent colour provides total coverage and intensity while maintaining scalp comfort. Its formula allows to equalize the colour evenly even on porous hair. The pigment penetrates the hair efficiently and is locked in for longlasting, vibrant colour.

FEATURES
Permanent hair colour.
Covers white air up to 100%.
Longlasting colour retention.
Intense colour vibrancy.
Works even on porous hair.
Absolute truetotuft results.

HOW TO USE
Mix the colour and developer at a ratio of 1: 1 for a normal colouring, or 1: 2 for a lighter shade.
VIRGIN HAIR: apply the mixture to lengths and ends, then to roots after 15 to 20 minutes.
COLOURED HAIR: apply the mixture to the regrowth, then to the lengths and tips after 15 to 30 minutes.
Leave as directed on instructions.
Rinse thoroughly, then wash and condition the hair.

product_name: BlondMe 800 Gram Bond Enforcing Premium Lightener Lift 9+
description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION

Blondme Bond Enforcing Premium Lightener 9+ is a high performance powder lightener. This is the first powder lightener to provide up to 9 levels of lift on natural and coloured hair. It offers perfect neutralisation thanks to it's antiyellowagents which directly target the pheomelanin in hair to avoid unwanted warm or yellow undertones.

FEATURES
Integrated bonding technology
Up to 9 levels of lift
Helps to protect the hair fiber during development for minimized hair breakage
Antiyellow agents to neutralize any warm undertones
Flexible mixing ratio
Easy workable consistency
Suitable for all technique

HOW TO USE
Always use in combination with BLONDME® Premium Developers.
Mix 1:1.5 to 1:2.5 (Ex: 30g BLONDME Premium Lightener 9+ and 4575 mL BLONDME Premium Developer).
OnScalp Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 2% (7 Vol.) or 6% (20 Vol.).
Application : BLONDME Premium Developer 9% (30 Vol.).
Apply to dry hair and let develop for 20 to 45 minutes.
Additional heat is not recommended.
Visually check progress during development time.

PROTIP
For gentle lightening and optimal time control, use BLONDME Premium Developer 2% (7 Vol.).
Check visually every 5 minutes.

description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION
This claybased powder lightener allows a precise application. The creamy consistency allows a smooth application and a seamless result. FEATURES
Claybased lightener
With bond enforcing technology

Up to 7 level of lift
Softtosolid formula

Ratio of 1: 1.5 or 1: 2 depending on the desired consistency
Apply on dry hair without additional heat

description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION
Schwarzkopf colour Remover allows to quickly erase previous colour while keeping the hair healthy. Integrated Bonding technology strengthens and protects the inside of the hair to reduce breakage. The remover is suitable for all types of coloured or depigmented hair and light up to 3 tones.

FEATURES:
Integrated Bonding technology
Removes colour in one step of 20 minutes or less

HOW TO USE:
Mix the complete content of part A and B with 60ml of developer
Apply evenly with a brush to dry hair starting on darker areas
Development Time: Up to 20 minutes.
Check every 5 minutes until desired result is achieved.
Rinse the hair and pat dry
Proceed with the new colour application

product_name: SKP Bond Enforcing Color Remover Kit
description:
All Schwarzkopf products available IN STORE ONLY. Store pre-orders and pick up is available. Contact your CanRad Sales Consultant or Customer Service for assistance.

DESCRIPTION
Schwarzkopf colour Remover allows to quickly erase previous colour while keeping the hair healthy. Integrated Bonding technology strengthens and protects the inside of the hair to reduce breakage. The remover is suitable for all types of coloured or depigmented hair and light up to 3 tones.

FEATURES:
Integrated Bonding technology
Removes colour in one step of 20 minutes or less

HOW TO USE:
Mix the complete content of part A and B with 60ml of developer
Apply evenly with a brush to dry hair starting on darker areas
Development Time: Up to 20 minutes.
Check every 5 minutes until desired result is achieved.
Rinse the hair and pat dry
Proceed with the new colour application
